Monkey and the crocodile

Once upon a time, in a forest, there lived a monkey who resided on a jamoon tree which was on the bank of a river. In the same forest, 
there also lived a crocodile and his wife. On the crocodile came to the banks of the river and rested under the same jamun tree. 
The kind hearted monkey offered him some fruits. The crocodile came back next day as he loved the fruits. As the day passed by 
the monkey and the crocodile became friends.